syncStatusSelect.upToDate:
**Functional Purpose**: Option for sync status filter indicating up-to-date items
**UI Location**: Solution list filters → Sync status dropdown
**When Users See This**: When the user opens the sync status filter dropdown
**Technical Context**: Represents 'up_to_date' status
**Current English**: "Up-to-date"
syncStatusSelect.outOfDate:
**Functional Purpose**: Option for sync status filter indicating out-of-date items
**UI Location**: Solution list filters → Sync status dropdown
**When Users See This**: When the user opens the sync status filter dropdown
**Technical Context**: Represents 'out_of_date' status
**Current English**: "Out-of-date"
syncStatusSelect.all:
**Functional Purpose**: Option for sync status filter to show all items regardless of sync status
**UI Location**: Solution list filters → Sync status dropdown
**When Users See This**: When the user opens the sync status filter dropdown
**Technical Context**: Represents 'undefined' status for filtering
**Current English**: "All"
syncStatusSelect.syncStatus:
**Functional Purpose**: Placeholder text for the sync status filter when no specific status is selected
**UI Location**: Solution list filters → Sync status dropdown
**When Users See This**: When the sync status filter is reset or initially loaded with no selection
**Technical Context**: Displayed when the filter value is 'undefined'
**Current English**: "Sync status"
